# Use Case - Service Client Automatisé

Workflow n8n pour automatiser la prise en charge client, extraction donnée, réponse IA (llama3, Claude fallback). Adaptation directe du workflow du repo ai-automation-stack.

```json
{
  "nodes": [
    {"type": "webhook", "parameters": {"path": "service-client"}},
    {"type": "llm", "model": "llama3"},
    {"type": "email", "parameters": {"to": "client"}}
  ],
  "connections": [[0,1],[1,2]],
  "description": "Automated customer service workflow, AI powered response and email integration."
}
```
